Les grandes routes maritimes

Travel Documentary hosted by Georges Pernoud, published by TV5Monde broadcasted as part of TV5Monde Thalassa series in 2015 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/8/89/Les-grandes-routes-maritimes-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
The great sea routes.

The sea routes, those invisible lines which unite men and make trade possible. Dedicated to the spice and cotton trades in the past, today they have become the symbols of globalisation. Explore some of these shipping lanes aboard a container-ship, a nuclear ice-breaker, a schooner and a navy vessel.
